EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear Sir / Madam,

Request your approval for change of contact details of customer as below:

Customer Name: {!Opportunity.Name}
Project Name: {!Opportunity.Project_Name_formula__c}
Project Unit: {!Opportunity.RW_Project_Unit__c}

Field  Existing Values  New Values
Primary Mobile No.  {!Opportunity.Mobile_Number__c}  {!Opportunity.Temp_Mobile__c}
Secondary Mobile No.  {!Opportunity.Secondary_Mobile_No_Masked__c}  {!Opportunity.Temp_Secondary_Mobile__c}
Primary Email  {!Opportunity.RW_Email__c}  {!Opportunity.Temp_Email__c}
Secondary Email  {!Opportunity.RW_Secondary_Email__c}  {!Opportunity.Temp_Secondary_Email__c}



Reply to this email with one of these words in the first line of the email message: APPROVE, APPROVED, YES, REJECT, REJECTED, NO  You can also add comments on the second line. Comments will be stored with the approval request in Salesforce CRM.

NOTE – this mail might have been sent to you for change in mobile / email on Account / Applicant details / SAP.

Alternatively, To approve or reject this item, click this link {!ApprovalRequest.Internal_URL}
